:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:512:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress image compression plugin? We&#8217;re guessing it&#8217;s because you want to optimize your pos for performance and search engine optimization (SEO).&#160; Let&#8217;s briefly look at some reasons installing an image compression plugin on your&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin/\">The Best WordPress Image Compression Plugin: 5 Excellent Options for 2022</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17651:\"<p>Are you looking for the best WordPress image compression plugin?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We&#8217;re guessing it&#8217;s because you want to optimize your pos for performance and search engine optimization (SEO).&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let&#8217;s briefly look at some reasons installing an image compression plugin on your website is an excellent idea.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Why Do You Need a WordPress Image Compression Plugin?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Visual assets like images make up an important part of the content on your posts and pages. Therefore, just like your written content, URLs, and other aspects of your website, your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-best-optimize-images-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"images need to be optimized for SEO\">images need to be optimized for SEO</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The best way to do that is to compress them.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Compressing your images also has the benefit of improving your page load speed, resulting in a positive user experience (UX). It also helps you meet <a href=\"https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/9205520?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Google\'s Web Core Vitals standards\">Google&#8217;s Web Core Vitals standards</a>. As a result, your website will rank higher, and you&#8217;ll drive more traffic.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sure, you can optimize your images by using powerful photo editing tools like Photoshop, but these can be costly and may require a bit more effort on your part.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s why considering an image compression plugin would be your best option. The best WordPress image compression plugins help make image optimization a breeze as they do most of the heavy lifting in the background.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>4 Factors to Consider as You Look for the Best WordPress Image Compression Plugin</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before we dive into our list of the best WordPress image compression plugins, let&#8217;s briefly look at what you should look for in an image compression plugin.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Support for Different File Types</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most important factors to consider as you look for an image compression plugin is whether it supports most popular image file types. Examples include PNG, JPG or JPEG, GIF, and WebP files.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Bulk Image Compression</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Image compression can be time-consuming, especially when working with hundreds of images. That&#8217;s why you should consider bulk compression as one of the features to look for in a WordPress image compression plugin. This feature will allow you to compress multiple images simultaneously, saving you a lot of time.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Different Compression Levels</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Image compression is a balancing act — you need to ensure you reduce an image&#8217;s file size without losing quality. That&#8217;s why you should prioritize a plugin that offers different compression levels. This will ensure that you can take a compression approach that will help you optimize each individual image. The two main different compression levels to consider are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><strong>Lossless compression</strong>: This allows you to compress your images without any loss to the quality of the image. However, your image file size won&#8217;t be reduced as much as it would with lossy compression.</li><li><strong>Lossy compression</strong>: This removes unnecessary data from an image to reduce the file size. Lossy compression usually gives you the most significant reduction in image file size.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>With that being said, let&#8217;s get you the best WordPress image compression plugin for your website, shall we?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>The Best WordPress Image Compression Plugin: Our Top 5 Picks</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to image compression plugins, you&#8217;ll be spoilt for choice as there are thousands to choose from. However, not all image compression plugins are the same. Some may slow down your website, conflict with other plugins, or downright fail to do what they promise.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To help you avoid the frustration that comes from trying out several image compression plugins, we&#8217;ve come up with this list of tried and tested ones.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/optimole/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Optimole\">Optimole</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/optimole/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Optimole\">Optimole</a> is one of the best WordPress image compression plugins on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/optimole/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"346\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-optimole.png\" alt=\"Optimole ranks as one of the best WordPress image compression plugins on the market.\" class=\"wp-image-69570\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-optimole.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-optimole-300x148.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-optimole-600x297.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Setting up Optimole requires creating an account and inserting your API keys. Once that&#8217;s done, using the plugin is straightforward, plus it gives you complete control over your image optimization. This makes the slight speed bump during the setup process worth it.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>One of Optimole&#8217;s most significant advantages is its dashboard — it&#8217;s easy to understand and features many useful settings. Speaking of settings, some image optimization settings you&#8217;ll find in Optimole&#8217;s dashboard include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Compression options</li><li>Large image sizing</li><li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-lazy-load-images-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"Lazy loading\">Lazy loading</a>&nbsp;</li><li>Watermarks</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>A notable feature you&#8217;ll also love is that Optimole uses an image CDN to serve up images. This ensures your images will load quickly and that each visitor gets served optimized images for their device.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another feature you&#8217;ll appreciate is that Optimole makes it easy to view all of your optimized images in a single dashboard. Doing so enables you to easily customize each image&#8217;s compression settings.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The only caveat with Optimole is that pricing isn&#8217;t as straightforward as other plugins on the list — it&#8217;s based on the number of visitors you receive. For example, the free plan supports up to 5,000 visitors per month. On the other hand, Paid plans start at $19.08/month with support for up to 25,000 visitors per month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/shortpixel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"ShortPixel Image Optimizer\">ShortPixel Image Optimizer</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/shortpixel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"ShortPixel Image Optimizer\">ShortPixel Image Optimizer</a> is another fantastic WordPress image compression plugin you should consider.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/shortpixel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"344\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-short-pixel.png\" alt=\"ShortPixel Image Optimizer qualifies to be the best WordPress image compression plugin on the market, thanks to its rich features. \" class=\"wp-image-69577\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-short-pixel.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-short-pixel-300x147.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-short-pixel-600x295.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>One reason ShortPixel Image Optimizer is one of the best WordPress image compression plugins&nbsp; is because it&#8217;s packed with advanced features. For example, the plugin allows you to choose compression formats. Another cool feature is image compression starts as soon you activate the plugin. It also stores your original images in a separate folder.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Like Optimole, ShortPixel Image Optimizer requires you to get an API key by providing your email address. Notable features you can expect from ShortPixel include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>3 compression options — lossy, lossless, and glossy</li><li>Compress up to 50 images at a go</li><li>Works on all file types (JPEG, PNG, GIF, and even PDFs)</li><li>Converts JPEG, PNG or GIF files to next-gen formats like WebP and AVIF</li><li>Convert PNG to JPEG and vice versa with a click of a button.</li><li>Integrates with Cloudflare</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The free version of ShortPixel Image Optimizer limits you to 10Mb or 300 images per month. However, you can sign up for their paid plans that start at $3.99/month (up to 7,000 images) billed annually to remove the limitations.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ewww-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"EWWW Image Optimizer\">EWWW Image Optimizer</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for an easy-to-use WordPress image compression plugin?</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ewww-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"EWWW Image Optimizer\">EWWW Image Optimizer</a> certainly fits that bill.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ewww-image-optimizer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"331\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-EWWW.png\" alt=\"EWWW is an easy to use WordPress image compression plugin, making it a fan favorite.\" class=\"wp-image-69578\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-EWWW.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-EWWW-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-EWWW-600x284.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Besides being super easy to use, EWWW also has the advantage of automatically optimizing images you upload. This makes it an excellent option for beginners or users who are pressed for time.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another benefit you&#8217;ll enjoy from this image compression plugin is that it allows for bulk image compression. Quality is also not compromised as you&#8217;ll hardly find a difference between original images and compressed ones.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What makes EWWW qualify as one of the best WordPress image compression plugins on our list?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Take a look at some of the plugin&#8217;s feature&#8217;s, and you&#8217;ll understand why:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Lazy loading</li><li>JS/CSS optimizations</li><li>Low-quality image placeholders (LQIP)</li><li>CDN image delivery</li><li>Auto-WebP</li><li>Automatic image scaling</li><li>Site speed audits</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best features you&#8217;ll love is that EWWW allows you to compress an unlimited number of images, no matter which plan you&#8217;re on. This even includes images generated by other WordPress plugins you&#8217;re using.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Speaking of plans, the plugin is also very affordable as paid plans start at $7/month.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/codecanyon-seo-friendly-images-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"SEO Friendly Images Pro\">SEO Friendly Images Pro</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#8217;re looking for an image compression plugin that does more than just compress your images, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/codecanyon-seo-friendly-images-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"SEO Friendly Images Pro\">SEO Friendly Images Pro</a> could be the solution you are looking for.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/codecanyon-seo-friendly-images-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"740\" height=\"357\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-seo-friendly-images-pro.png\" alt=\"SEO Friendly Images Pro certainly qualifies to be named the best WordPress image compression plugin.\" class=\"wp-image-69579\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-seo-friendly-images-pro.png 740w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-seo-friendly-images-pro-300x145.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-seo-friendly-images-pro-600x289.png 600w\" sizes=\"100vw\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>As the name suggests, SEO Friendly Images Pro was explicitly designed to help users <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-hacks-to-grow-your-traffic/\" title=\"boost their SEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">boost their SEO</a>. That&#8217;s why it has several features beyond just image size optimization. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>For example, SEO Friendly Images Pro automatically optimizes all your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-write-alt-text-for-images-for-seo-3-easy-tips/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"image alt and title attributes\">image alt and title attributes</a>. Other notable features of the plugin include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Superfast lazy loading</li><li>Supports content images, thumbnails, and images from third-party plugins</li><li>Auto-updates with WordPress&#8217;s update mechanism</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>With SEO Friendly Images Pro, optimizing your images for SEO becomes a breeze.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Wondering how much this powerful image compression plugin will cost you?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Expect to pay $20 for the regular license, which comes with six months of support.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://tinypng.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"TinyPNG\">TinyPNG</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another plugin you should consider as you look for the best WordPress image compression plugins is <a href=\"https://tinypng.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"TinyPNG\">TinyPNG</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://tinypng.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"293\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-tinypng.png\" alt=\"TinyPNG should be on your radar as you look for the best WordPress image compression plugin.\" class=\"wp-image-69582\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-tinypng.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-tinypng-300x126.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin-tinypng-600x251.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>TinyPNG automatically optimizes new images you upload. The plugin can also easily bulk-optimize images you already have on your site. Another advantage of TinyPNG is that it allows you to set a maximum width and/or height for your images, allowing for automatic resizing of large images. To help you get a better understanding of what the plugin can do, here are some of its features:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>No file size limits</li><li>Preserve image metadata like copyrights, creation date, location, e.t.c</li><li>Supports all image file types (including animations)</li><li>WooCommerce compatible</li><li>Multisite support with a single API key</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The free version of TinyPNG is limited to 100 images/month. If you&#8217;re a power user and want to remove the limit, you can upgrade to the paid plans.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best WordPress Image Compression Plugins: Part of Your SEO Toolkit</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Image compression is no longer an option — what with Google prioritizing websites that load fast and users preferring the same, you have no choice but to make image compression a part of your SEO strategy.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s why an image compression plugin must be part of your SEO toolkit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Speaking of SEO toolkits, besides an image compression plugin, you should also consider installing the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-plugins-for-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"best WordPress SEO plugin\">best WordPress SEO plugin</a>. Doing so will help ensure that every aspect of your website is optimized.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>What&#8217;s the best WordPress SEO plugin?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>According to over 3 million users, it&#8217;s AIOSEO. Go ahead and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"download AIOSEO today\">download AIOSEO today</a>!</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin/\">The Best WordPress Image Compression Plugin: 5 Excellent Options for 2022</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-image-compression-plugin/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n