";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:436:\"<p>On the hunt for the best Instagram Plugin for WordPress? With over 2 billion monthly active users, Instagram is one of the most popular social media platforms. With such a large following, it makes sense to integrate the social media&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress/\">The Best Instagram Plugin for WordPress: Our Top 7</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21397:\"<p>On the hunt for the best Instagram Plugin for WordPress?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With over <a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2021/12/14/instagram-surpasses-2-billion-monthly-users.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"2 billion monthly active users\">2 billion monthly active users</a>, Instagram is one of the most popular social media platforms. With such a large following, it makes sense to <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-integrate-social-media-into-your-website/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"integrate the social media platform\">integrate the social media platform</a> with your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>To do that, you&#8217;ll need to find the best Instagram plugin for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, with thousands of them on the market, finding the right one for you can be quite a daunting task.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>That&#8217;s why we&#8217;ve compiled this list of the seven best Instagram plugins you should consider.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Why Do You Need the Best Instagram Plugin for WordPress?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Social media is a powerful platform that can help you boost brand awareness and grow your business. One of the rising stars among social media platforms is Instagram. Because of that, installing an Instagram plugin is a no-brainer. It helps makes your Instagram marketing much easier. This is because an excellent Instagram plugin will help you easily (among other things):</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Embed your Instagram feed on your site</li><li>Create interactive slides to engage website visitors</li><li>Share WordPress posts on Instagram</li><li>Run Instagram giveaways right on your website</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The best Instagram plugins for WordPress also have the advantage of being lightweight, thereby ensuring that your <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-cache-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"site load speed\">site load speed</a> is not affected.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If social media marketing is part of your overall marketing strategy (as it should be), then you need the right tools to help you succeed. An Instagram plugin is one such tool.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With that being said, let&#8217;s help you get the best Instagram plugin for your WordPress website.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best Instagram Plugin for WordPress — 7 to Consider</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ready to give your website a makeover with the best Instagram plugin for WordPress?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Then let&#8217;s dive right into our top seven.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/smashballoon-instagram-feed/\" title=\"Instagram Feed by Smash Balloon\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Instagram Feed Pro by Smash Balloon</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/smashballoon-instagram-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"Instagram Feed Pro\">Instagram Feed Pro</a> by Smash Balloon is by far the best Instagram plugin for WordPress on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/smashballoon-instagram-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"402\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-instagram-feed-pro.png\" alt=\"Instagram Feed Pro by Smash Balloon is undoubtedly the best Instagram plugin for WordPress. \" class=\"wp-image-69157\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-instagram-feed-pro.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-instagram-feed-pro-300x172.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-instagram-feed-pro-600x345.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>With over 1.3 million active installs (including big brands like Coca-Cola and Mariah Carey), Instagram Feed Pro is the highest-rated Instagram feed plugin for WordPress. The numbers and positive reviews are testaments that it&#8217;s the best Instagram plugin for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Smash Balloon has a free version of the plugin that lets you easily add and customize your Instagram feed on your WordPress site. However, despite being free, you still get a ton of great built-in features.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, if you need to up your Instagram game, you&#8217;ll need to upgrade to the pro version of Instagram Feed. Some of the features you&#8217;ll unlock are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Multiple photo layout choices</li><li>Image resizing</li><li>Hashtag feed display</li><li>Create shoppable feeds</li><li>Lightbox option with built-in social sharing buttons</li><li>Display multiple Instagram feeds, including Instagram Stories</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The best part about Instagram Feed Pro is that it&#8217;s super-easy to set up, even if you&#8217;re not tech-savvy. You also don&#8217;t need an Instagram Developer account to get the best Instagram integration with your website.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another great feature you&#8217;ll love about Smash Balloon&#8217;s Instagram plugin is its smart feed cache and backup functionality. For one, it allows you to show Instagram photos on your site without compromising your website&#8217;s speed. Also, you can still display your images even if the Instagram API goes down.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>How much will a powerful Instagram plugin like Instagram Feed Pro cost you?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As if it can&#8217;t get any better, you&#8217;ll be glad to know Instagram Feed Pro starts at a low&nbsp; $49/year.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <a href=\"https://rafflepress.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"RafflePress\">RafflePress</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://rafflepress.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"RafflePress\">RafflePress</a> is another excellent candidate for the best Instagram plugin for WordPress award.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://rafflepress.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"550\" height=\"252\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-raffle-press.png\" alt=\"RafflePress is another plugin that ranks as one of the best Instagram plugins for WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-69159\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-raffle-press.png 550w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-raffle-press-300x137.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Unlike most other Instagram plugins on this list, RafflePress is primarily geared toward running contests and giveaways. RafflePress makes it extremely easy to set up contests that prompt your visitors to take specific actions on social media, including Instagram. You can also run Instagram contests that encourage your followers to visit <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/posts-vs-pages-in-wordpress/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"particular pages\">particular pages</a> on your website or even sign up for your email list.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Some features that make RafflePress standout as one of the best Instagram plugins for WordPress include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Viral giveaway templates</li><li>Drag-and-drop giveaway builder</li><li>Fraud protection</li><li>Viral sharing</li><li>Tracking and analytics</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the most significant advantages of using RafflePress to grow your audience and build brand awareness is its super easy use. The free version gives you a no-obligation to try out this powerful Instagram plugin for WordPress without making any commitments. However, if you want to unlock the full power of the plugin, you&#8217;ll have to sign up for the paid plans, which start at $49/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/codecanyon-instagram-theatre/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Instagram Theatre\">Instagram Theatre</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another excellent Instagram plugin for WordPress that should be on your radar is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/codecanyon-instagram-theatre/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Instagram Theatre\">Instagram Theatre</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/codecanyon-instagram-theatre/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"251\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-instagram-theatre.png\" alt=\"When looking for the best Instagram plugin for WordPress, you\'ll definitely come across Instagram Theatre.\" class=\"wp-image-69160\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-instagram-theatre.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-instagram-theatre-300x108.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-instagram-theatre-600x215.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>As one of the best Instagram plugins for WordPress, Instagram Theatre allows you to easily display your Instagram pictures on your website. The plugin offers users several layout options and three fully responsive templates, among many other features. With Instagram Theatre, you can also specify a tag to search from the Instagram API using the Tag Instagram Feed feature. This allows you to select the images to display on your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Other features you&#8217;ll enjoy from Instagram Theatre include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Intuitive, easy to use admin panel</li><li>Several customization options</li><li>Pull images from multiple users</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>One thing you&#8217;ll love about Instagram Theatre is that it comes with several visual effects. These help keep your website visitors entertained and engaged. They also help encourage them to follow you on Instagram, helping you grow your followership.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A regular license of Instagram Theatre will set you back $16, making it one of the most affordable Instagram plugins for WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/modula-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Modula\">Modula</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another gallery plugin that works well as an Instagram plugin for WordPress is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/modula-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Modula\">Modula</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/modula-gallery/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"320\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-modula.png\" alt=\"Modula definitely qualifies to be included in this list of the best Instagram plugins for WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-69162\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-modula.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-modula-300x137.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-modula-600x274.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Like Envira, Modula is a WordPress Gallery plugin that allows you to beautifully display photographs on your site. The beauty of Modula is that you can easily integrate it with your social media platforms, including Instagram. When you do so, you can display media from your Instagram feed. Some features that help make Modula one of the best Instagram plugins for WordPress include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Filter options</li><li>Custom layouts</li><li>Image resizing and optimization</li><li>Protected galleries</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Modula is also very responsive, making your images look fantastic on all devices. Responsiveness is also helpful for SEO. For better engagement, Modula also lets your visitors browse through your galleries using filters.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As for pricing, you can get started with Modula for $39/year.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/revive-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Revive Old Posts\">Revive Old Posts</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/revive-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Revive Old Posts\">Revive Old Posts</a> is an Instagram plugin with a twist in that it&#8217;s more of a schedular. It enables you to share previously published blog content on your favorite social networks, including Instagram.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/revive-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"396\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-revive-old-posts.png\" alt=\"Revive Old Posts is another excellent WordPress plugin for Instagram.for\" class=\"wp-image-69164\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-revive-old-posts.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-revive-old-posts-300x170.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-revive-old-posts-600x339.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Revive Old Posts gives you a lot of freedom regarding the posts you want to share on Instagram. For example, you can set a custom schedule based on date range, post categories or tags. You can also use Revive Old Posts to share photos directly from your media library to your Instagram account. Other features to expect include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Custom hashtags pulled from <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/the-difference-between-tags-and-categories/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"tags and categories\">tags and categories</a></li><li>Tracking via Google Analytics</li><li>Automated posting</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Revive Old Posts has helped many brands save time on their social media marketing, thanks to its ease of use.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If Revive Old Posts sounds like the best Instagram plugin for WordPress for you, expect to pay $75/year for it.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/codecanyon-grace-wordpress-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Grace\">Grace</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for an Instagram plugin that makes it easy for you to display your Instagram pictures on your website?</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/codecanyon-grace-wordpress-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Grace\">Grace</a> is yet another plugin that enables you to do just that.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/codecanyon-grace-wordpress-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"398\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-grace.png\" alt=\"Grace could be the best Instagram plugin for WordPress you\'re looking for, thanks to it being feature-rich.\" class=\"wp-image-69366\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-grace.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-grace-300x171.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-grace-600x341.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Grace is a premium WordPress plugin designed to help you create a graceful Instagram feed on your WordPress website. The plugin enables you to aggregate and embed posts from single or multiple Instagram accounts right onto your website.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>When it comes to giving your feed a unique look, the customization options of the plugin are almost infinite. You can easily change any aspect of your Instagram feed galleries, from the color of your post to the layouts and even re-positioning elements. Other features you can look forward to with the plugin include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Post-approval</li><li>Template builder</li><li>Several gallery layout options</li><li>Content filtering</li><li>Translation ready</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Grace is a feature-rich plugin, making it one of the best Instagram plugins for WordPress. It’s also one of the most affordable too, with a regular license going for $19.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>7. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wd-instagram-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"10Web Social Photo Feed\">10Web Social Photo Feed</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re looking for an easy way to add an Instagram feed to your posts or pages, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wd-instagram-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"10Web Social Photo Feed\">10Web Social Photo Feed</a> could be the solution you’re looking for.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wd-instagram-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"355\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-10web-social-photo-feed.png\" alt=\"10Web Social Photo Feed is another excellent option when looking for the best Instagram plugin for WordPress.\" class=\"wp-image-69371\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-10web-social-photo-feed.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-10web-social-photo-feed-300x152.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/best-instagram-plugin-for-wordpress-10web-social-photo-feed-600x304.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>10Web Social Photo Feed comes with both free and paid versions, both of which are more than capable of enabling you to effectively integrate your Instagram account with your website. Examples of features to expect from the plugin include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Custom layouts</li><li>Instagram galleries</li><li>Display individual or mixed feeds</li><li>Conditional filters</li><li>Infinite scroll</li><li>Advanced Lightbox</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll also love that 10Web Social Photo Feed comes with a built-in widget that enables you to display your Instagram posts in your WordPress sidebar.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Pricing for 10Web Social Photo Feed starts at $85 for a lifetime access license.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best Instagram Plugin for WordPress — Which Should You Pick?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Finding the perfect Instagram plugin for your WordPress website is never an easy task. Sometimes, you&#8217;ll have to install and test many different plugins to find one you can commit to. Hopefully, this list will save you tons of time tinkering around with the plethora of Instagram plugins on the market.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, which plugin from this list takes the crown as the best Instagram plugin for WordPress?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Overall, Smash Balloon&#8217;s <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/smashballoon-instagram-feed/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"Instagram Feed Pro\">Instagram Feed Pro</a> is the winner. Ticking most boxes, including ease of use and value for money, among others, you won&#8217;t regret installing this plugin. However, if you&#8217;re looking for a plugin to help schedule and publish your posts to Instagram, then <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/revive-post/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" title=\"Revive Old Posts\">Revive Old Posts</a> is the perfect one for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Boost Brand Visibility and Grow Your Business with the Best Instagram Plugin for WordPress</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Social media is a powerful tool for boosting brand awareness and growing your business. That&#8217;s why installing the best Instagram plugin on your WordPress website is a no-brainer. That&#8217;s especially seeing as the platform has over 2 billion users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, social media alone is not enough to help you get your brand in front of your target audience. Search engine optimization also plays a significant role. That&#82