;s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:41978:\"<p>On the hunt for the best WordPress themes for SEO?</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/seo-best-practices/\">Search engine optimization</a> (SEO) plays a massive role in the success of your website and business. That&#8217;s why every element of your website must contribute to your overall SEO strategy — including your WordPress theme. It&#8217;s for this reason that you must ensure you use the best WordPress themes for SEO for all your websites.&nbsp; Doing so will give you a better chance of ranking and driving traffic to your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What is a WordPress Theme?</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A WordPress theme is a pre-coded file that provides the front-end styling of your website. It determines how your website will ultimately look. Your theme of choice can control significant elements like the layout to seemingly minor features like the color of your hyperlinks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>A WordPress theme allows you to customize your website to suit the vision and purpose you have for your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>But more than aesthetics, your theme can also add functionality to your WordPress website.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Most users love WordPress because it comes ready to use straight out of the box. That includes a lot of free themes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>However, when choosing the right theme to use for your website, you need to look beyond looks. You must also consider the fact that your theme has an impact on your website’s SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Your theme must both look good and play a role in boosting your SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>21 Best WordPress Themes for SEO&nbsp;</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Creating SEO-optimized content is not easy. That&#8217;s why, to better increase the chances of your content being seen by your target audience, you must ensure your website is primed for success. One way of doing that is by using an SEO-friendly theme. These are themes that are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Lightweight</li><li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-cache-plugin/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Load fast</a></li><li>Provide a positive user experience (UX)</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>To help you choose one that’s perfect for you, we’ve compiled this list of the 21 best WordPress themes for SEO you need to know in 2022.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/elegantthemes-divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Divi</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/elegantthemes-divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Divi </a>is one of the most popular SEO-friendly website themes on the market because of its versatility. You can use it to build virtually any kind of website.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/elegantthemes-divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"414\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-divi.png\" alt=\"Divi is one of the best WordPress themes for SEO.\" class=\"wp-image-67333\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-divi.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-divi-300x177.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-divi-600x355.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Another reason for Divi’s popularity is its ease of use, thanks to the drag-and-drop builder. You can use it to build your website visually — no code required. Other features to expect from Divi include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>40+ website modules</li><li>800+ pre-built layouts</li><li>Easy customization</li><li>Shape dividers</li><li>Filters and effects</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Above all, thanks to its minimalistic coding, Divi is a lightweight and super-fast theme designed with SEO in mind. As a result, you can use it to build websites that search engines and users love.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>2. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">OceanWP</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another WordPress theme built with SEO in mind is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">OceanWP</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"308\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-oceanwp.png\" alt=\"OceanWP is another fantastic WordPress theme for SEO to consider. \" class=\"wp-image-67334\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-oceanwp.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-oceanwp-300x132.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-oceanwp-600x264.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>One advantage of OceanWP is that it comes with beautiful, super clean demo content. This will help you have a better picture of what your website will look like. It also helps build your website faster as you can choose the content that best suits your niche and tweak it to your liking.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>OceanWP also has the advantage of being a fast theme, resulting in your website satisfying <a href=\"https://web.dev/vitals/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Google’s Web Vitals requirements</a>. It also ensures a positive user experience (UX) for users. Both are essential to a robust SEO strategy. Notable features of the theme include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Easy demo import</li><li>Top-notch speed</li><li>WooCommerce integration</li><li>Full-screen scrolling</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>For international SEO, OceanWP comes translation-ready, enabling you to create a multilingual website easily.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>3. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/astra-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Astra</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/astra-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Astra</a> is one name that will pop up when you’re looking for the best WordPress themes for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/astra-wordpress-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"464\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-astra.png\" alt=\"Astra is one of the best WordPress themes for SEO to consider.\" class=\"wp-image-67335\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-astra.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-astra-300x199.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-astra-600x398.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Astra comes pre-loaded with several starter sites catering to different business niches. These make it easy to find the perfect template for your website easily.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You’ll find it easy to customize the theme as Astra comes with powerful design options. It also supports popular drag-and-drop page builders like <a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SeedProd</a>, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/wpbakery-page-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">WPBakery</a>, etc. Page builders give you more freedom to be creative and realize the dreams you have for your website. Astra also comes with other impressive features that include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Powerful design options</li><li>Sticky header</li><li>Various site layouts</li><li>Several typography option</li><li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pagination-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Post pagination</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>What makes Astra one of the best WordPress themes for SEO is its lightweight build and super-fast performance. You can also extend your Astra-themed website’s performance by pairing it with powerful SEO plugins like All in One SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>4. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/superb-themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">EcoCoded</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>As the name suggests, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/superb-themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">EcoCoded</a> is a WordPress theme that prides itself in helping users build eco-friendly websites.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/superb-themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"310\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-ecocoded.png\" alt=\"EcoCoded is one of the best WordPress themes for SEO, especially for those who are environmentally conscious..\" class=\"wp-image-67337\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-ecocoded.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-ecocoded-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-ecocoded-600x266.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>One factor that makes EcoCoded one of the best WordPress themes for SEO is clean, compressed code. Add to that the fact that the theme automatically optimizes your images, and you’ll have a lightweight website that loads super fast. Other notable features:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Google Fonts</li><li>Demo content importer</li><li>Sidebar layout</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>The only caveat to EcoCoded is that it’s a no-frills theme. This means you can only use it for basic sites that don’t feature a lot of fancy animation, frameworks, and fonts.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Despite not having as many bells and whistles as other WordPress themes on this list, EcoCoded is a fantastic theme that packs a punch as far as SEO is concerned.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>5. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Ultra</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another theme that’s popular with SEO-savvy website builders is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Ultra</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"394\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-ultra.png\" alt=\"When looking for the best WordPress themes for SEO, Ultra should top your list.\" class=\"wp-image-67339\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-ultra.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-ultra-300x169.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-ultra-600x338.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Ultra is a multi-purpose theme you can use to build stunning websites. It comes with beautiful demo sites (with over 60 professional layouts) you can import with one click. Tweaking them to your fancy is also easy, and you can customize everything from the header right to the footer. You also get 12 builder add-ons for free when you buy Ultra, giving you more flexibility to create your website to your desired specifications.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For a lightweight and ultra-fast WordPress theme, Ultra comes with a lot of bells and whistles that include, among others:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Responsive layouts</li><li>Slider backgrounds</li><li>Video backgrounds</li><li>Parallax scrolling</li><li>Custom styling options</li><li>Animation</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Ultra definitely ranks among the top for an easy-to-use theme that fits well into your SEO strategy.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>6. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/artisanthemes-indigo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Indigo</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re looking to build a website that’s fun, fresh, and futuristic, <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/artisanthemes-indigo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Indigo</a> is the theme for you.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/artisanthemes-indigo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"332\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-indigo.png\" alt=\"Indigo is another amazing WordPress theme that\'s SEO-friendly.\" class=\"wp-image-67340\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-indigo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-indigo-300x142.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-ind