s://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-satchmo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-satchmo-300x186.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-satchmo-600x371.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Featuring a minimalist design and ultra-lightweight code, it’s a fast-loading theme that will keep both search engines and your audience happy. Satchmo also comes with video support, allowing you to diversify your content. You’ll also enjoy features like:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Episode sliders</li><li>Easy to customize using WordPress Customizer</li><li>RTL support</li><li>One-click demo import</li><li>Supports over 900 Google fonts</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Satchmo makes it so easy for you to build a professional website, whether you’re tech-savvy or not. As a result, you can focus on more pressing issues &#8211; creating content.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>18. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mythemeshop-sociallyviral/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">SociallyViral</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Another SEO-friendly WordPress theme to have on your radar is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mythemeshop-sociallyviral/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">SociallyViral</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mythemeshop-sociallyviral/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-socially-viral.png\" alt=\"SociallyViral is an excellent SEO-friendly WordPress theme that can help grow your audience.\" class=\"wp-image-67390\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-socially-viral.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-socially-viral-300x154.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-socially-viral-600x309.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>SociallyViral was designed for businesses that rely on audience building, as the name suggests. Socially Viral comes packed with features designed to boost social shares, traffic, and ultimately, revenue. Core features to expect include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Options panel</li><li>Display trending posts</li><li>Adsense optimized</li><li>4 different loading effects</li><li>Subscription box</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Every element of the SociallyViral theme was designed to encourage engagement. As a result, your posts stand a better chance of reaching a wider audience.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>19. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/cssigniter-koehn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Koehn</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Showcasing your business products, achievements, and capabilities is the best way to generate new leads and get more customers. That’s why you must leverage themes like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/cssigniter-koehn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Koehn</a> to build your website.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/cssigniter-koehn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"342\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-koehn.png\" alt=\"Koehn is a WordPress them designed for local businesses in the manufacturing, construction, fabrication, and related industries.\" class=\"wp-image-67391\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-koehn.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-koehn-300x147.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-koehn-600x293.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Koehn is a WordPress them designed for local businesses in the manufacturing, construction, fabrication, and related industries. That’s because it was designed to make your products the heroes of your brand story. This is thanks to its clean and minimalist design. Other features that make Koehn shine include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Drag-and-drop design</li><li>Custom widgets</li><li>Flexible layout options</li><li>Page builder integration</li><li>Powerful theme customizer</li><li>Full-screen slider&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Impressing potential clients becomes easier when you have a website that allows your products to shine. An SEO-ready WordPress theme like Koehn helps you do just that.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>20. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/athemes-sydney-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Sydney</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/athemes-sydney-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Sydney</a> is another fantastic WordPress SEO theme to put on your radar if you’re looking for the best WordPress themes for SEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/athemes-sydney-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"260\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-sydney-pro.png\" alt=\"Sydney is a versatile theme that also ranks as one of the best WordPress themes for SEO.\" class=\"wp-image-67392\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-sydney-pro.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-sydney-pro-300x111.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-sydney-pro-600x223.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Due to its versatility, you can use the theme to create any kind of website ranging from corporate businesses to creative agencies to small-scale industries and everything in-between. Whether you’re a pro or novice, you’ll love Sydney’s flexibility as it allows you to customize your website to suit your vision. Besides versatility and flexibility, you can also expect the below features from Sydney:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Multiple layout options</li><li>Slider, static, and video headers</li><li>Different menu layouts </li><li>WPML ready</li><li>Button styling</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>For an SEO-friendly multi-purpose WordPress theme, look no further than Ombrello.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>21. <a href=\"https://noor.pixeldima.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Noor</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Minimalism and versatility are elements that make for an SEO-friendly WordPress theme. <a href=\"https://noor.pixeldima.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Noor</a> does both exceptionally well.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https://noor.pixeldima.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"rel=nofollow noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"700\" height=\"298\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-noor.png\" alt=\"Noor is an elegant theme that qualifies to be on the best WordPress themes for SEO list.\" class=\"wp-image-67393\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-noor.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-noor-300x128.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/best-wordpress-theme-for-seo-noor-600x255.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Noor is a WordPress theme featuring fresh creative design and an intuitive drag-and-drop page builder.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>With Noor, you can <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-website-builder-for-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">build beautiful SEO-optimized websites</a> thanks to the theme&#8217;s unlimited layouts. Creating an e-commerce store is also easy, thanks to Noor’s WooCommerce integration.&nbsp;Other features to expect are:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>WPML compatibility</li><li>RTL languages support</li><li>Elements and modules</li><li>Unlimited layouts</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p> So no matter the type of website you want to build, Noor will help you make it a reality.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Best WordPress Themes for SEO — Take Your Pick</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing the right theme for a website build can be quite a daunting task. This is true for both novices and professionals. Armed with this selection of the best WordPress themes for SEO, picking the perfect theme for your next build should be easier.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you’ve built your website using the best WordPress theme for SEO, don’t forget to install the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/yoast-vs-jetpack-vs-all-in-one-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">best WordPress SEO plugin</a> — AIOSEO. With AIOSEO, optimizing your website for people and search engines is a cinch, and you don’t even have to touch a single line of code.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>So, go ahead and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">download AIOSEO today</a>.&nbsp;</p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-themes-for-seo/\">21 Best WordPress Themes for SEO in 2022 (Compared)</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://aioseo.com/best-wordpress-themes-for-seo/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";